description: Another grey day. I have to get used to getting my ass up more early to catch more daylight. After a success-less search in-front of the university I decided to try my luck in front of a bus stop. So after about three minutes I saw a cute guy standing alone. I approached him not knowing yet if he was old enough. He had a special chaotic hairstyle which I like really very much and more luckily he was already 18. He studied to become a car-mechanic and was heading to visit his mother at work. He was very open-minded and wasn´t even shocked when our little conversation started to become more "intimate" if you know what I mean. He didn´t hesitate to show me his dick and it took only five minutes and 8 000 CZK to convince him to suck me off...
title: Czech Hunter 218
